<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV95">
<l>aṭakkarumpu laṉkaḷainta ṭakkiyācai yāmavai</l>
<l>toṭakkaṟuttu vantuniṉṟo ḻiṟkaṇiṉṟa veṉṉainī</l>
<l>viṭakkaruti meyceyātu mikkorācai yākkiluṅ</l>
<l>kaṭaṟkiṭanta niṉṉalālor kaṇṇilēṉem maṇṇalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taming the five sense organs that are hard to tame, severing attachment</l>
<l>to objects of desire, I came and stood steadfast in Your service.</l>
<l>Thnking of giving up [me who did that], [You] did not act truthfully and</l>
<l rend="indent">created excessive desire [for other things].</l>
<l>Despite [that], I do not have a protector other than You, who lay on the ocean,</l>
<l rend="indent">o superior [Lord]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
